{"text_id":14995,"tokens":["On"," the"," Mapping"," of"," Time","-","Dependent"," Den","sities"," onto"," Pot","entials"," in"," Quantum"," Mechanics","\n\n","In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," the"," problem"," of"," mapping"," time","-","dependent"," densities"," onto"," potentials"," in"," quantum"," mechanics","."," The"," goal"," is"," to"," develop"," a"," systematic"," approach"," for"," computing"," the"," potential"," energy"," of"," a"," quantum"," system"," from"," its"," time","-","dependent"," density","."," To"," this"," end",","," we"," employ"," a"," novel"," methodology"," that"," combines"," the"," concepts"," of"," quantum"," gradient"," flows"," and"," Wass","erstein"," distances","."," Our"," approach"," enables"," us"," to"," construct"," a"," one","-","to","-","one"," mapping"," between"," the"," time","-","dependent"," density"," and"," the"," potential"," energy",","," providing"," a"," new"," perspective"," on"," the"," relationship"," between"," these"," two"," fundamental"," concepts"," in"," quantum"," mechanics","."," Through"," numerical"," simulations"," and"," analytical"," calculations",","," we"," demonstrate"," the"," accuracy"," and"," efficiency"," of"," our"," method",","," showcasing"," its"," applicability"," to"," a"," range"," of"," quantum"," systems",","," including"," Schr\u00f6dinger","'","s"," equation"," and"," quantum"," many","-","body"," problems","."," Our"," results"," not"," only"," shed"," light"," on"," the"," long","-","standing"," issue"," of"," reconstru","cting"," potentials"," from"," densities"," but"," also"," open"," up"," new"," avenues"," for"," the"," study"," of"," quantum"," systems",","," particularly"," in"," the"," context"," of"," quantum"," machine"," learning"," and"," control","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}